          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1660640676625-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, chop your <strong>parsley</strong> finely, including the stalks</p><p>Chop your <strong>cherry tomatoes</strong> in half</p><p>Crumble your <strong>goats' cheese</strong> into rough bite-sized pieces</p><p>Cut your <strong>lemon[s]</strong> into 2 wedges per person</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1660640679046-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1660640679046-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1660640679046-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1660640679046-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1660640679046-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine the juice of 1<strong> lemon wedge </strong>per person with your <strong>balsamic vinegar</strong> and 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [2 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil </strong>in a small bowl – this is your <strong>zesty</strong> <strong>dressing</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>zesty</strong> <strong>dressing</strong> to the pan with <strong>half</strong> the <strong>chopped parsley </strong>(save the rest for garnish!)<strong> </strong>and a very generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>warm</strong> <strong>pepper, lentil & white bean salad</strong></p><p>Wash your <strong>salad</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1660640681862-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1660640681862-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1660640681862-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1660640681862-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1660640681862-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>warm</strong> <strong>pepper, lentil & white bean salad</strong> with the <strong>halved cherry tomatoes</strong> and<strong> salad </strong>over the top</p><p>Garnish with the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>chopped parsley</strong>, a <strong>lemon wedge </strong>and an extra drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Sprinkle over your<strong> goats'</strong> <strong>cheese</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
